<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xml:lang="en"><generator uri="https://gohugo.io/" version="0.85.0">Hugo</generator><title type="html">autocomplete on ilo</title><link href="https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/tags/autocomplete/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="HTML"/><link href="https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/tags/autocomplete/index.xml" rel="alternate" type="application/rss+xml" title="RSS"/><link href="https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/tags/autocomplete/atom.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" title="Atom"/><updated>2021-07-12T04:56:11+00:00</updated><id>https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/tags/autocomplete/</id><entry><title type="html">CLI Autocomplete</title><link href="https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/usage/cli-autocomplete/?utm_source=atom_feed" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id>https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/usage/cli-autocomplete/</id><published>2020-04-13T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2020-04-13T00:00:00+00:00</updated><content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>The <code>ilo generate-completion</code> command generates autocompletion configuration for shells such as <a href="https://www.gnu.org/software/bash/">bash</a> and <a href="https://www.zsh.org/">zsh</a>.</p>
<p>In order to get autocomplete working in your shell, execute the following snippet:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="chroma"><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">$ <span class="nb">source</span> &lt;<span class="o">(</span>ilo generate-completion<span class="o">)</span>
</code></pre></div><p>See the integration pages for various <a href="../../integration/shells">shells</a> for details.</p>
<p>Once enabled you can use the <code>&lt;TAB&gt;</code> key to autocomplete ilo commands and their options:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="chroma"><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell"><span class="c1"># autocomplete commands</span>
$ ilo s&lt;TAB&gt;
$ ilo shell

<span class="c1"># autocomplete options</span>
$ ilo shell --p&lt;TAB&gt;
$ ilo shell --pull
</code></pre></div>]]></content><category scheme="https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/categories/usage" term="usage" label="usage"/><category scheme="https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/tags/autocomplete" term="autocomplete" label="autocomplete"/></entry></feed>